[
  {
    "startTime": 0.32,
    "endTime": 12.6,
    "text": "(acoustic guitar and piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.32,
    "endTime": 26.66,
    "text": "(piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.76,
    "endTime": 31.44,
    "text": "I took the supermarket flowers from the window sill"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.84,
    "endTime": 36.38,
    "text": "I threw the day old tea from the cup"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.12,
    "endTime": 47.459999999999994,
    "text": "packed up the photo album Mathew had made, memories of a life that's been loved"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.24,
    "endTime": 53.34,
    "text": "Took the \"get well soon\" cards and stuffed animals,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.34,
    "endTime": 58.900000000000006,
    "text": "poured the old ginger beer down the sink"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.54,
    "endTime": 68.42,
    "text": "Dad always told me, \" Don't you cry when your down.\" but mum there's a tear every time that I blink"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.28,
    "endTime": 80.12,
    "text": "Oh I'm in pieces its tearin' me up but I know a heart that's broke is a heart that's been loved"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.12,
    "endTime": 88.86,
    "text": "So I'll sing hallelujah, you were an angel in the shape of my mum"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.24,
    "endTime": 93.05999999999999,
    "text": "When I fell down you'd be there holdin' me up,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.06,
    "endTime": 103.58,
    "text": "spread your wings as you go and when God takes you back he'll sing, \"Hallelujah, your home\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.6,
    "endTime": 111.78,
    "text": "(piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.88,
    "endTime": 117.19999999999999,
    "text": "I fluffed the pillows, made the bed, and stacked the chairs up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.32,
    "endTime": 122.44,
    "text": "Folded your nightgown neatly in a case"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.96,
    "endTime": 133.72,
    "text": "John said he'd drive then put his hand on my cheek, and wiped a tear from the side of my face"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.36,
    "endTime": 143.82000000000002,
    "text": "I hope that I see the world as you did, 'cause I know a life with love is a life that's been lived"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.82,
    "endTime": 147.23999999999998,
    "text": "So I'll sing hallelujah"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.24,
    "endTime": 152.62,
    "text": "you where an angel in the shape of my mum"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.92,
    "endTime": 159.17999999999998,
    "text": "when I fell down you'd be there holding me up, spread your wings as you go"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.18,
    "endTime": 166.9,
    "text": "and when God takes you back he'll sing, \" Hallelujah your home,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.1,
    "endTime": 176.38,
    "text": "(piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.78,
    "endTime": 184.74,
    "text": "oooooooh"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.1,
    "endTime": 188.92,
    "text": "Hallelujah your home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.14,
    "endTime": 195.55999999999997,
    "text": "(piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.56,
    "endTime": 199.36,
    "text": "Hallelujah your home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.36,
    "endTime": 208.76000000000002,
    "text": "(piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.94,
    "endTime": 216.96,
    "text": "Hallelujah, you where an angel in the shape of my mum"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.32,
    "endTime": 221.68,
    "text": "You got to see the person that I've become"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.68,
    "endTime": 231.56,
    "text": "spread you wings and I know that when God took you back he said, \"Hallelujah your home.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.12,
    "endTime": 235.14000000000001,
    "text": "Oh God"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.18,
    "endTime": 237.085,
    "text": "I'm such a mess"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.085,
    "endTime": 239.92000000000002,
    "text": "and the dogs are barking outside have ruined my cover"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.92,
    "endTime": 241.05999999999997,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.06,
    "endTime": 242.0,
    "text": "(sniffs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.92,
    "endTime": 251.11999999999998,
    "text": "I was thinkin' 'bout you, thinkin' 'bout me, thinkin' 'bout us what we gon' be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.12,
    "endTime": 256.94,
    "text": "Opened my eyes it was only just a dream"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.94,
    "endTime": 260.64,
    "text": "so I traveled back down that road"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.8,
    "endTime": 270.5,
    "text": "Will she come back? no one knows, I realized it was only just a dream"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.06,
    "endTime": 273.22,
    "text": "I was at the top"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.22,
    "endTime": 276.34000000000003,
    "text": "and now its like I'm in the basement number one spot"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.34,
    "endTime": 278.84,
    "text": "now you found you a replacement"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.0,
    "endTime": 281.9,
    "text": "I swear now that I can't take it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.9,
    "endTime": 285.2,
    "text": "knowing somebody's got my baby"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.595,
    "endTime": 288.425,
    "text": "now you ain't around baby I can't think"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.425,
    "endTime": 291.685,
    "text": "I should've put it down, should've got that ring"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.685,
    "endTime": 294.4,
    "text": "'Cause I can still feel it in the air"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.4,
    "endTime": 300.38,
    "text": "See your pretty face run my fingers through your hair, my lover, my life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.38,
    "endTime": 303.42,
    "text": "my baby, my wife"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.42,
    "endTime": 305.36,
    "text": "you left me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.36,
    "endTime": 306.94,
    "text": "I'm tied"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.94,
    "endTime": 309.2,
    "text": "'cause i know that it just aint right"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.2,
    "endTime": 315.84,
    "text": "I was thinking bout you, thinkin' bout me\nThinkin' bout us, what we gon' be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.84,
    "endTime": 321.9,
    "text": "Opened my eyes, it was only just a dream"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.32,
    "endTime": 328.92,
    "text": "So I traveled back, down that road\nWill she come back, no one knows"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.92,
    "endTime": 335.2,
    "text": "I realized it was only just a dream"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.24,
    "endTime": 338.38,
    "text": "If you've ever loved somebody put your hands up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.58,
    "endTime": 341.56,
    "text": "If you've ever loved somebody put your hands up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.74,
    "endTime": 347.04,
    "text": "now they're gone and you wish that you could give them everything"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.8,
    "endTime": 351.52000000000004,
    "text": "If you've ever loved somebody put your hands up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.64,
    "endTime": 355.32,
    "text": "If you've ever loved somebody put your hands up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.76,
    "endTime": 360.48,
    "text": "now you wish that you could give them every thing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.48,
    "endTime": 367.28000000000003,
    "text": "I was thinking bout you, thinkin' bout me\nThinkin' bout us, what we gon' be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.34,
    "endTime": 373.73999999999995,
    "text": "Opened my eyes, it was only just a dream"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.74,
    "endTime": 374.52,
    "text": "oh"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.74,
    "endTime": 377.58,
    "text": "traveled back down that road"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.82,
    "endTime": 388.21999999999997,
    "text": "Will she come- Will she come back? no one knows, it was only just a dream"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.42,
    "endTime": 391.12,
    "text": "(piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.68,
    "endTime": 394.92,
    "text": "Open my eyes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 394.92,
    "endTime": 398.04,
    "text": "It was only just a dream"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.58,
    "endTime": 406.14,
    "text": "it was only just a dream"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.7,
    "endTime": 430.53999999999996,
    "text": "(piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.54,
    "endTime": 435.12,
    "text": "I know I'm probably better off on my own"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.12,
    "endTime": 438.52,
    "text": "Than lovin' a man who didn't know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438.52,
    "endTime": 442.58,
    "text": "What he had when he had it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.34,
    "endTime": 449.34,
    "text": "And I see the permanent damage you did to me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449.34,
    "endTime": 455.82,
    "text": "Never again, I just wish I could forget when it was magic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.84,
    "endTime": 465.34,
    "text": "I wish it wasn't four am, standing in the mirror\nSaying to myself, you know you had to do it I know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465.74,
    "endTime": 471.12,
    "text": "The bravest thing I ever did was run"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.04,
    "endTime": 477.08000000000004,
    "text": "Sometimes, in the middle of the night, I can feel you again"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.66,
    "endTime": 484.0,
    "text": "And I just miss you, and I just wish you were a better man"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 484.68,
    "endTime": 488.58,
    "text": "And I know why we had to say goodbye"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 488.62,
    "endTime": 490.78000000000003,
    "text": "Like the back of my hand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491.22,
    "endTime": 497.5,
    "text": "And I just miss you, and I just wish you were a better man"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497.96,
    "endTime": 501.21999999999997,
    "text": "A better man"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 502.5,
    "endTime": 507.6,
    "text": "I know I'm probably better off all alone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.6,
    "endTime": 514.52,
    "text": "Than needing a man who could change his mind at any given minute"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 514.52,
    "endTime": 521.1,
    "text": "And it's always on your terms\nI'm hanging on every careless word"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 521.5,
    "endTime": 525.34,
    "text": "Hoping it might turn sweet again"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 525.5,
    "endTime": 528.16,
    "text": "Like it was in the beginning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.78,
    "endTime": 534.68,
    "text": "But your jealousy, I can hear it now\nYou're talking down to me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.68,
    "endTime": 543.2199999999999,
    "text": "like I'll always be around\nYou push my love away like it's some kind of loaded gun"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 543.22,
    "endTime": 547.26,
    "text": "Boy, you never thought I'd run"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 547.64,
    "endTime": 553.04,
    "text": "Sometimes, in the middle of the night, I can feel you again"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 553.04,
    "endTime": 559.48,
    "text": "And I just miss you, and I just wish you were a better man"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.48,
    "endTime": 566.5600000000001,
    "text": "And I know why we had to say goodbye\nLike the back of my hand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 566.56,
    "endTime": 573.2399999999999,
    "text": "And I just miss you, and I just wish you were a better man"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 573.36,
    "endTime": 580.44,
    "text": "A better man"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 580.64,
    "endTime": 587.58,
    "text": "(piano)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.76,
    "endTime": 593.9399999999999,
    "text": "And I hold onto this pride because these days it's all I have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 594.28,
    "endTime": 603.88,
    "text": "And I gave to you my best and we both know you can't say that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 603.98,
    "endTime": 606.94,
    "text": "You can't say that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.9,
    "endTime": 639.1,
    "text": "(guitar)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639.1,
    "endTime": 639.94,
    "text": "Come up to meet you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639.94,
    "endTime": 640.44,
    "text": "Tell you I'm sorry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 640.44,
    "endTime": 640.94,
    "text": "You don't know how lovely you are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 640.94,
    "endTime": 641.44,
    "text": "I had to find you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.44,
    "endTime": 641.94,
    "text": "Tell you I need you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.94,
    "endTime": 642.44,
    "text": "Tell you I set you apart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 642.44,
    "endTime": 642.94,
    "text": "Tell me your secrets"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 642.94,
    "endTime": 643.44,
    "text": "And ask me your questions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643.44,
    "endTime": 643.94,
    "text": "Oh let's go back to the start"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643.94,
    "endTime": 644.44,
    "text": "Running in circles, coming up tails"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 644.44,
    "endTime": 644.94,
    "text": "Heads on a science apart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 644.94,
    "endTime": 645.44,
    "text": "Nobody said it was easy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 645.44,
    "endTime": 645.94,
    "text": "It's such a shame for us to part"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 645.94,
    "endTime": 646.44,
    "text": "Nobody said it was easy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.44,
    "endTime": 646.94,
    "text": "No one ever said it would be this hard"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.94,
    "endTime": 647.44,
    "text": "Oh take me back to the start"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.44,
    "endTime": 647.94,
    "text": "I was just guessing at numbers and figures"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.94,
    "endTime": 648.44,
    "text": "Pulling your puzzles apart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 648.44,
    "endTime": 648.94,
    "text": "Questions of science, science and progress"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 648.94,
    "endTime": 649.44,
    "text": "Do not speak as loud as my heart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 649.44,
    "endTime": 649.94,
    "text": "Tell me you love me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 649.94,
    "endTime": 650.44,
    "text": "Come back and haunt me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 650.44,
    "endTime": 650.94,
    "text": "Oh and I rush to the start"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 650.94,
    "endTime": 651.44,
    "text": "Running in circles, chasing our tails"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.44,
    "endTime": 651.94,
    "text": "Coming back as we are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.94,
    "endTime": 652.44,
    "text": "Nobody said it was easy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.48,
    "endTime": 652.8000000000001,
    "text": "Oh it's such a shame for us to part"
  },
  {
